          <h4 style="margin:4px 0">Easter-egg: Konami</h4>
          <p style="margin:4px 0;opacity:.9">Up, Up, Down, Down, Left, Right, Left, Right, B, A â€” do it anytime to unlock a secret theme and 500 points.</p>
